create 3 instances 
and provide connection between it by making the entry of hostname and ip in /etc/hosts file
generate ssh key and copy to the target machine under authorized keys
install ansible on controller machine
make the entry in /etc/ansible
[dev-servers]
ansible-target
[prod-servers]
ansible-target2

       ip a s
    2  vim /etc/hosts
    3  cd /etc/ansible
    4  vim hosts
    5  vim basic-apache.yaml
    6  cd
    7  ssh-keygen
    8  cat .ssh/id_rsa.pub
    9  cd /etc/ansible
   10  vim basic-apache.yaml
   11  cd ..
   12  mv fstab /etc/ansible
   13  cd ansible
   14  ll
   15  vim basic-apache.yaml
       vim index.html
   16  ansible-playbook basic-apache.yaml --syntax-check
   17  ansible-playbook basic-apache.yaml -C
   20  ansible-playbook basic-apache.yaml
